                            <comment id="13998874" author="stack" created="Thu, 15 May 2014 16:18:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Resolving as invalid.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This kind of question best belongs on the user or dev lists.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Yeah, the notiion is that you can ask to run with more closers.  We don&apos;t list every config in the hbase-default.xml because it would overwhelm and confuse.  Some configs are in code only.  If you have gone to the trouble of reading the code, then you&apos;ll likely understand what the particular minor config can do for you.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
